<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="urge-vt">urge <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɜːdʒ/    美 /ɜːrdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>驱策；驱赶：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I urged the elephant deeper into the forest.
我赶着大象进到森林的更深之处。</p><footer>2014 重庆</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>催促；力劝</strong></h4>
<p>to advise or try hard to persuade sb to do sth：</p>
<ul>
<li>urge sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They urged me to eat the strange food. 
他们怂恿我吃那种奇怪的食物。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>极力主张</strong></h4>
<p>to recommend sth strongly：</p>
<ul>
<li>urge + that ... (should) do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He urged that we (should) take such steps. 
他极力主张我们采取这些措施。</p></div></div>